      "content": "that makes sense. so if the financial support isn't really hitting the mark for the smaller players, it feels like these regs end up being a massive hurdle for them compared to the big corps. basically, do these environmental policies just favor large-scale industry while making it harder for small local manufacturers to stay competitive?",
